    <h4 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3-fill"></i> How It Works</h4>
      </div>
     <div class="card-body">
    <ol class="lead">
     <li><strong>Start Session:</strong> User initiates a conversation</li>
         <li><strong>Ask Questions:</strong> System asks minimal required questions</li>
      <li><strong>Parse Input:</strong> Natural language processing extracts values</li>
              <li><strong>Evaluate Rules:</strong> Decision engine checks immediate and conditional rules</li>
                <li><strong>Derive Traits:</strong> Calculate additional traits (min, max, count)</li>
  <li><strong>Recommend:</strong> Provide the best-fit outcome</li>
         </ol>

